query:
INSERT INTO _departments (id, name, code, parent_code, created_at, updated_at)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                name = EXCLUDED.name,
                code = EXCLUDED.code,
                parent_code = EXCLUDED.parent_code,
                updated_at = EXCLUDED.updated_at
